Technology Development (ATD)$$, $$This project matures and demonstrates a geospatial rapid position and navigation solution in Global Positioning System (GPS) degraded and denied environments.
Research focuses on using onboard sensors and high-resolution digital terrain geospatial alternative solution based upon Visual Three-Dimensional (3-D) Terrain
