multi-domain operational environment.

Work in this project complements Program Element (PE) 0602146A (Network C3I Technology) / Project CV4 (Pathfinder 3D Applied Technology).

Work in this project is performed by the United States Army Engineer Research and Development Center Geospatial Research Laboratory.

