international opportunities.
FY 2027 Plans:
Continue software development work for ICADS 7, finalize test planning, and start formal test campaign. The development
activities are a continuation of planned contractor iteration reviews and deliveries of hardware and software. Additional
system integration and checkout is also planned during this time in order to support testing and ensure final system delivery
is operationally ready. This period includes any remaining test planning work needed to support upcoming activities. Formal
Government test will also start in FY 2027 for Developmental Test (DT).
