A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
The Program Office is developing the Universal Ground NUDET Detection System (NDS) Terminal (UGNT) 7 modernization effort (Project 672808) for Guardians across
Missile Warning and Missile Tracking (MW/MT) mission area. As a result, the Service will improve readiness and operational reach of existing force structure.

The UGNT 7 modernization effort is the Survivable/Endurable (S/E) system capable of processing United States Nuclear Detonation (NUDET) data from the next-gen
